Package Description
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon
This is the core package for the game.
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon.collision
This is the package for collissions between game objects like Sprites.
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon.level
This is the package for all levels.
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon.level.editor
This is the package for the games level editor.
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon.menu
This is the package for the game menus.
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon.scenes
This is the package for all game Scenes.
de.zabuza.jumpPokemon.sprites
This is the package for all game Sprites.
de.zabuza.physicEngine
This is the package of the portable PhysicEngine.
de.zabuza.physicEngine.forms
This is the package of all physically Forms from the portable PhysicEngine.
de.zabuza.soundEngine
This is the package of the portable SoundEngine.
de.zabuza.soundEngine.mixer
This is the package of all sound mixers from the portable SoundEngine.
de.zabuza.soundEngine.sample
This is the package of all sound samples, players and loaders from the portable SoundEngine.
